00:14:21,130 --> 00:14:23,150
It is the will of Ishbala.

277
00:14:23,790 --> 00:14:25,750
He is an accursed alchemist—

278
00:14:25,750 --> 00:14:29,260
and what's worse, he now 
seeks the Philosopher's Stone.

279
00:14:30,100 --> 00:14:32,880
Why is alchemy so bad?

280
00:14:32,880 --> 00:14:35,060
I mean, your own 
right arm has a circle,

281
00:14:35,060 --> 00:14:38,480
though it's one 
I've never seen before.

282
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:44,610
It is a brand I received when I took on 
the calling to destroy all State Alchemists.

283
00:14:45,820 --> 00:14:48,030
And as for the Philosopher's Stone,

284
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:51,330
he isn't looking for it 
to use it in battle.

285
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:55,430
It's in order to return 
my body to me.

286
00:14:56,930 --> 00:15:00,040
You don't know the terror 
of the Philosopher's Stone!

287
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:01,520
We do!

288
00:15:01,520 --> 00:15:05,300
There's a legend that destruction befalls those who seek the Philosopher's Stone, right?

289
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:08,080
But if we were afraid of that, 
we'd never get our hands on anything.

290
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:11,530
Come to mention it, I heard that Ishbal also perished

291
00:15:11,530 --> 00:15:14,210
because it came too close 
to the Philosopher's Stone.

292
00:15:14,210 --> 00:15:15,260
No!

293
00:15:16,430 --> 00:15:18,950
Ishbal did not perish.

294
00:15:19,780 --> 00:15:21,480
It was destroyed!

295
00:15:22,030 --> 00:15:23,270
Brother!

296
00:15:23,930 --> 00:15:26,280
Brother! Open up!

297
00:15:26,950 --> 00:15:28,250
Brother!

298
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:34,970
Brother, is it true?

299
00:15:34,970 --> 00:15:36,650
You've tried alchemy?

300
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:46,440
I failed.

301
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:48,550
It cannot be done this way.

302
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,970
However,

303
00:15:49,970 --> 00:15:51,780
there is still the Philosopher's Stone.

304
00:15:53,470 --> 00:15:59,560
Brother, alchemy is a heretical practice that alters the creation that God has given us!

305
00:15:59,770 --> 00:16:00,640
But...

306
00:16:01,410 --> 00:16:03,060
our god, Ishbala...

307
00:16:03,770 --> 00:16:06,370
will not bring her 
back to life for us.

308
00:16:18,810 --> 00:16:19,800
Brother!

309
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,220
The military...

310
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:28,670
They mean business...

311
00:16:29,180 --> 00:16:31,150
Brother, it's too dangerous here!

312
00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:40,060
Brother!

313
00:16:40,850 --> 00:16:43,150
I have finally begun to see...

314
00:16:43,660 --> 00:16:46,100
What the Philosopher's Stone is...

315
00:16:46,100 --> 00:16:50,280
Why Ishbala has forbidden it to us...

316
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:51,940
Brother...

317
00:16:51,940 --> 00:16:53,400
Stop this already!

318
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:57,750
The enemy is trying to destroy us 
with this power of the Devil!

319
00:16:57,750 --> 00:16:59,910
Yes, it's true.

320
00:17:00,630 --> 00:17:02,540
Ishbal will be destroyed.

321
00:17:03,670 --> 00:17:08,540
That is something that has been preordained.

322
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:12,010
I believed that if I could obtain the Philosopher's Stone,

323
00:17:12,010 --> 00:17:14,150
she would come back to life

324
00:17:14,150 --> 00:17:17,050
and Ishbal would be saved.

325
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:20,490
However, it is for that purpose

326
00:17:20,490 --> 00:17:23,470
that Ishbal must be destroyed.

327
00:17:24,070 --> 00:17:25,060
Brother...

328
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,060
Brother!

329
00:17:42,250 --> 00:17:44,580
Brother!

330
00:17:50,390 --> 00:17:51,600
Scar-san...

331
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:58,370
I know that the Philosopher's Stone 
can be made from people's bodies.

332
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:01,100
We came to verify that.

333
00:18:01,940 --> 00:18:04,760
If that's true, then we...

334
00:18:04,760 --> 00:18:06,310
My, my...

335
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:11,800
There sure are 
a lot of intruders today.

336
00:18:12,090 --> 00:18:13,340
Who are you?

337
00:18:13,940 --> 00:18:14,940
You!

338
00:18:15,370 --> 00:18:17,490
Why are you making that face?

339
00:18:18,940 --> 00:18:20,240
My brother...

340
00:18:20,950 --> 00:18:22,580
Did he succeed?

341
00:18:22,930 --> 00:18:24,320
What do you mean?

342
00:18:24,320 --> 00:18:25,990
Can I eat them?

343
00:18:27,070 --> 00:18:30,150
The armored one would be bad for your stomach.

344
00:18:30,150 --> 00:18:31,290
I'll do my best!

345
00:18:32,150 --> 00:18:33,590
Homunculus...

346
00:18:36,540 --> 00:18:38,050
Homunculus?

347
00:18:38,770 --> 00:18:39,800
They couldn't be...!

348
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:45,560
So the military falsified your execution

349
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:48,310
and had you create Chimeras here?

350
00:18:49,850 --> 00:18:51,560
Not just Chimeras...

351
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:55,520
I'm doing research on 
a number of things...

352
00:18:55,520 --> 00:18:58,070
that cannot be made 
public knowledge.

353
00:18:58,630 --> 00:19:03,580
Spirit bonding, and other tricks 
you can't do with ordinary alchemy.

354
00:19:03,580 --> 00:19:05,430
You may have become a Chimera,

355
00:19:05,430 --> 00:19:08,080
but you still have your complete memory from when you were human.

356
00:19:08,540 --> 00:19:11,030
Who has that kind of skill?

357
00:19:11,030 --> 00:19:15,090
Doctor Marcoh? 
Basque Grand? Someone else?

358
00:19:16,460 --> 00:19:19,430
Answer me! 
Who the hell runs this place?!

359
00:19:25,860 --> 00:19:27,600
Please don't look at them.

360
00:19:28,430 --> 00:19:30,190
They're quite bashful.

361
00:19:45,260 --> 00:19:46,490
Nina?

362
00:19:46,940 --> 00:19:51,200
They still cannot keep their shape when exposed to the open air.

363
00:19:53,900 --> 00:19:58,230
There's no way you're able to 
perform human transmutation.

364
00:19:58,230 --> 00:20:02,190
You created a Chimera... 
to look like Nina?

365
00:20:02,190 --> 00:20:05,000
But each time, I failed,

366
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:07,480
and in the end, 
I wound up in this form.

367
00:20:08,830 --> 00:20:11,350
However, I'm just one step away...

368
00:20:12,620 --> 00:20:14,230
Just one step away...

369
00:20:16,660 --> 00:20:19,070
One... step away?

370
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:05,100
The unfinished Philosopher's Stone material that Doctor Marcoh had...

371
00:21:05,100 --> 00:21:10,120
You must already know that 
it alone has considerable power.

372
00:21:17,130 --> 00:21:21,930
If this large amount of unfinished material could be completely refined,

373
00:21:21,930 --> 00:21:23,950
you would have a Philosopher's Stone.

374
00:21:35,550 --> 00:21:36,440
Too slow!

375
00:21:42,670 --> 00:21:46,950
However, no one 
has yet been successful.

376
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:49,830
It is impossible...

377
00:21:50,220 --> 00:21:51,600
for any ordinary alchemist.

378
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:57,000
I am...

379
00:21:58,710 --> 00:21:59,880
I am...

380
00:22:01,630 --> 00:22:04,490
no ordinary alchemist.

381
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:16,790
We are still crying out

382
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:16,790
bokura wa ima demo sakenderu

383
00:22:21,980 --> 00:22:26,850
You squeeze your right hand, as if to reassure yourself

384
00:22:21,980 --> 00:22:26,850
tashikameru you ni nigirishimeta migite

385
00:22:26,850 --> 00:22:31,700
Go on, take those annoying rules and dash them away!

386
00:22:26,850 --> 00:22:31,700
uzattai housoku o buchikowashite yuke

387
00:22:31,850 --> 00:22:36,840
If it comes down to having to rest your wounded feet,

388
00:22:31,850 --> 00:22:36,840
kizutsuita ashi o yasumaseru gurai nara

389
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:41,730
you've gotta keep moving forward, if only just a step!

390
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:41,730
tatta ippo demo koko kara susume

391
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:46,500
We've pushed our way

392
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:46,500
through the twisting winds

393
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:46,500
yuganda kaze o kaki wakete

394
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:51,630
and gotten beyond the cold sky

395
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:51,630
tsumetai sora o oikoshite

396
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:58,400
Yet we still continue to wander

397
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:58,400
soredemo mada samayoi tsuzuketeru

398
00:23:01,940 --> 00:23:06,570
We always find ourselves crying out

399
00:23:01,940 --> 00:23:06,570
bokura wa itsudemo sakenderu

400
00:23:06,570 --> 00:23:11,910
Just continuing to believe is not the answer

401
00:23:06,570 --> 00:23:11,910
shinji tsuzukeru dake ga kotae janai

402
00:23:11,910 --> 00:23:16,620
We must bare our weaknesses and wounds,

403
00:23:11,910 --> 00:23:16,620
yowasa mo kizu mo sarake dashite

404
00:23:16,620 --> 00:23:21,300
and continue to struggle,

405
00:23:16,620 --> 00:23:21,300
or nothing will ever turn out!

406
00:23:16,620 --> 00:23:21,300
mogaki tsuzukenakereba hajimaranai

407
00:23:21,300 --> 00:23:29,000
Break on through to the other side of the door!

408
00:23:21,300 --> 00:23:29,000
tsukiyabure tobira no mukou e

409
00:23:29,120 --> 00:23:34,600
To the other side of the door!

410
