00:23:40,340 --> 00:23:43,580
Episode 22: "Created Human"

416
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,520
Homunculus—

417
00:23:45,550 --> 00:23:48,570
a pseudo-human, 
created through alchemy.

418
